<h2>Fizz Bang!!!</h2>

<ul>
	<li class="no-bullet">Numbers from 1 to 100.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
	<li>If the number is evenly divisible by 3, print "Fizz" in blue.</li>
	<li>If the number is evenly divisible by 5, print "Bang" in green.</li>
	<li>If the number is evenly divisible by 3 AND 5, print "FIZZ BANG!!!" in red.</li>
	<li>If the number is NOT evenly divisable by 3 or 5, print the number.</li>
</ul>

